# REST Client configuration for VSCode

### Environment Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost
@ingestPort = 8000
@predictorPort = 8090
@entitlementsPort = 4010
@apiKey = dev-key-12345

### Local Development Endpoints

## Ingest API Health
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{ingestPort}}/health

### List Events
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{ingestPort}}/events

### Create Event
POST {{baseUrl}}:{{ingestPort}}/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "UFC Fight Night",
  "status": "scheduled",
  "start_at": "2026-05-15T18:00:00Z"
}

---

## Predictor API Health
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{predictorPort}}/health

### Get Fight Prediction
POST {{baseUrl}}:{{predictorPort}}/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fighter_a": {
    "name": "Alex Silva",
    "stats": {
      "wins": 15,
      "losses": 2,
      "strike_accuracy": 0.65,
      "takedown_accuracy": 0.72
    }
  },
  "fighter_b": {
    "name": "Jordan Davis",
    "stats": {
      "wins": 12,
      "losses": 3,
      "strike_accuracy": 0.58,
      "takedown_accuracy": 0.65
    }
  }
}

---

## Entitlements API Health
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{entitlementsPort}}/health

### Create Checkout Session (Stripe)
POST {{baseUrl}}:{{entitlementsPort}}/checkout/session
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "user_id": "user-123",
  "event_id": "event-456",
  "price_tier": "standard"
}

### Issue Entitlement Token
POST {{baseUrl}}:{{entitlementsPort}}/tokens/issue
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "user_id": "user-123",
  "event_id": "event-456",
  "token_ttl": 3600
}

---

## Monitoring & Observability

### Prometheus Metrics
GET http://localhost:9090/api/v1/query?query=up

### Grafana Dashboard
GET http://localhost:3001

### Vault Secrets
GET http://localhost:8200/v1/secret/dfc
X-Vault-Token: root

---

## Database Queries (via REST)

### Get Database Health
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{ingestPort}}/health/db

### Get Event Count
GET {{baseUrl}}:{{ingestPort}}/events/count

---

## Production Cloud Endpoints

@cloudBaseUrl = https://api.datafightcentral.com
@prodApiKey = {{env PROD_API_KEY}}

### Production: Ingest Health
GET {{cloudBaseUrl}}/ingest/health
Authorization: Bearer {{prodApiKey}}

### Production: Create Event
POST {{cloudBaseUrl}}/ingest/events
Authorization: Bearer {{prodApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "PPV Event",
  "status": "live",
  "start_at": "2026-06-01T20:00:00Z"
}
